From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: kierandrewett <kieran@drewett.dev>
Date: Fri, 3 Jul 2026 09:38:43 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] gnoblin-panel: register the gnoblin panel in the loader +
 panels list

Adds the two upstream registrations for the gnoblin overlay panel
(panels/gnoblin/, copied in via scripts/copy-overlay.sh):
  - shell/cc-panel-loader.c: an extern decl + one PANEL_TYPE("gnoblin", ...)
    row so the panel is discoverable and its gnome-gnoblin-panel.desktop is
    honoured by cc_panel_loader_fill_model().
  - panels/meson.build: 'gnoblin' added to the panels list so the static lib is
    built and linked.

The panel implementation itself is gnoblin overlay source, not a patch.
---
 panels/meson.build      | 1 +
 shell/cc-panel-loader.c | 2 ++
 2 files changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/panels/meson.build b/panels/meson.build
index 07c7733..2c55535 100644
--- a/panels/meson.build
+++ b/panels/meson.build
@@ -9,6 +9,7 @@ panels = [
   'background',
   'color',
   'display',
+  'gnoblin',
   'mouse',
   'multitasking',
   'notifications',
diff --git a/shell/cc-panel-loader.c b/shell/cc-panel-loader.c
index 28a1671..019bce3 100644
--- a/shell/cc-panel-loader.c
+++ b/shell/cc-panel-loader.c
@@ -39,6 +39,7 @@ extern GType cc_bluetooth_panel_get_type (void);
 extern GType cc_color_panel_get_type (void);
 extern GType cc_date_time_panel_get_type (void);
 extern GType cc_display_panel_get_type (void);
+extern GType cc_gnoblin_panel_get_type (void);
 extern GType cc_keyboard_panel_get_type (void);
 extern GType cc_mouse_panel_get_type (void);
 extern GType cc_multitasking_panel_get_type (void);
@@ -93,6 +94,7 @@ static CcPanelLoaderVtable default_panels[] =
 #endif
   PANEL_TYPE("color",            cc_color_panel_get_type,                NULL),
   PANEL_TYPE("display",          cc_display_panel_get_type,              NULL),
+  PANEL_TYPE("gnoblin",          cc_gnoblin_panel_get_type,              NULL),
   PANEL_TYPE("keyboard",         cc_keyboard_panel_get_type,             NULL),
   PANEL_TYPE("mouse",            cc_mouse_panel_get_type,                NULL),
   PANEL_TYPE("multitasking",     cc_multitasking_panel_get_type,         NULL),
